title: Swimming with Sea Lions in Lima
description:
Our desires are to show the nature specifically in the islands of Callao especially the great colony of sea lions, penguins and guano birds. For which it we have modern speed boats where you will make excursions and other nautical activities.

We will pick you up from your hotel or apartment and take you outside Lima in a province called Callao, where our most important port of the Capital is located, here we will enter to La Punta and take you out to sea in comfortable and safe speedboats to visit the islands of Callao among which are, San Lorenzo, Palomino, Cabinzas and the Fronton.

Participating in the island excursion, watching fishing, rock formations, swimming in the colony with sea lions, birdwatching, diving with sea lions, are the main nautical activities to which we will take you with total security. Children and adults alike enjoy the waterfront and adventure sport also.

At the end of this excursion your driver will take you back to your hotel.
